metadata.name: Wobble #1
metadata.description: 2,222 generative Wobbles are ready to wobble their way into the Wobbleverse. These cute, stylish, friendly Wobbles are here to bring good vibes and positivity to the Web3 space. With a simple roadmap including an exclusive merch store and Wobble products, Wobbles aims at building a recognisable brand that everyone can enjoy. We aim to bring back what this space is all about.. fun times!
